    <h3 class="shelf__h2">
      General FAQ
    </h3>
    <hr class="shelf__hr" />
    
    <ul class="shelf__list">
      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">What’s a .TV network?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>A collection of videos, organized into one or more individual channels called Rolls.</li>
          <li>An expression of your tastes, interests, opinions, whims</li>
          <li>An experience, designed from the ground up to get out of your way and let the content speak for itself</li>
          <li>A threat to traditional TV networks and their refusal to innovate</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">Why would I want my own .TV network?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>Build the brand of your company</li>
          <li>Build your personal brand</li>
          <li>Organize your favorite videos as you come across them on the Internet</li>
          <li>Show your friends the best stuff</li>
          <li>Create something beautiful the world should be watching, instead of traditional TV</li>
          <li>Create something to put on at a party</li>
          <li>It's exactly what you'd like to see at http://YourName.tv</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">How do I curate to my .tv network?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>With our Chrome plugin and bookmarklet, you can curate directly from any website.</li>
          <li>You can also curate anything in Shelby when you’re watching somebody else's Roll or your own Stream.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">What’s the Stream?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>Your stream is an incoming collection of video.  It’s the one place in Shelby that houses content from every Roll you follow.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">What’s a Roll?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>It’s a themed collection of video (the “channel” within the .tv network).</li>
          <li>You can follow other Rolls on Shelby</li>
          <li>Your .TV network can be made up of multiple rolls to showcase different types of content.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">What about Twitter and Facebook?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>Shelby shows you a stream of videos.  These videos come from Shelby Roll’s you follow and your Twitter or Facebook friends (if you’ve linked those accounts).</li>
          <li>You can also share to Twitter and Facebook when you roll a video.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">What about iPad?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>We think TVs and YouTube have become way too complicated.  They stopped being enjoyable when they stopped focusing on you, the viewer.  We won’t stand for that.</li>
          <li>So we’re working on bringing Shelby to more devices, making sure you can relax and enjoy it at home.</li>
          <li><em>Stay tuned...</em></li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3 class="shelf__h3">Did you really just make that pun?</h3>
        <ul class="shelf__list">
          <li>Yes.  And we’re not apologizing.  We love it.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
    
    
